24-02-2013 Version 0.1.0
========================

12-03-2013 Version 0.1.2
========================
Added workaround for KDE compositing causing jittery graphics. It is only used
if Xlib development libraries are installed. Uses _KDE_NET_WM_BLOCK_COMPOSITING

31-05-2013 Version 0.1.3
========================
Added support for framebuffer consoles that cannot change mode. Removed KDE
compositing workaround - users can disable compositing themselves if need be.

01-09-2013 Version 1.0
======================
Made a few little changes.

18-05-2014 Version 1.1
======================
Fixed a bug that drew score outside the main window when using framebuffer.

